 *
 * AUTHOR: Darwyn Peachy
 *
 * REFERENCES:
 *    _Texturing and Modeling: A Procedural Approach_, by David S. Ebert, ed.,
 *    F. Kenton Musgrave, Darwyn Peachey, Ken Perlin, and Steven Worley.
 *    Academic Press, 1994.  ISBN 0-12-228760-6.
